# @blog-post: Trilingual Blog Generator

Transform markdown input into 3 HTML blog posts (ES/EN/PT) with automatic index updates.

## Auto-Trigger
Activate this protocol when:
- User provides markdown file (*.md) with @ reference in blog workspace
- User explicitly invokes "@blog-post"
- User requests "generate blog post", "publish post", or similar intent
- Context indicates blog publishing workflow

## Input/Output
- **IN:** Plain markdown (no frontmatter)
- **OUT:** 3 HTML files + 3 updated indexes

